ta</h3><p>扁平化项目、分享、反馈、动态列表的item组件。</p><h3><a href=\"https://github.com/weifuchuan/JFinalAPP#102-beta\"></a>1.0.2-beta</h3><p>可触摸的组件更改为全平台都使用涟漪反馈效果。</p><h3><a href=\"https://github.com/weifuchuan/JFinalAPP#101-beta\"></a>1.0.1-beta</h3><p>未登录下，提交回复跳到登录页。</p><h3><a href=\"https://github.com/weifuchuan/JFinalAPP#100-beta\"></a>1.0.0-beta</h3><p>Covering almost all features of jfinal.com .</p><h2><a href=\"https://github.com/weifuchuan/JFinalAPP#license\"></a>License</h2><p><a href=\"https://github.com/weifuchuan/JFinal/blob/master/LICENSE\">Apache License 2.0</a></p>\n			</div>',1539567655563,13,2,NULL,7),
